title: Syrian army moves on last rebel enclave
text:
Syrian army moves on last rebel enclave 8:26pm IST - 01:07 
Syrian government and allied forces have launched an assault on Douma, the last rebel enclave in eastern Ghouta. Jaish al-Islam is holding out there after all other rebel groups left. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
